    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The quality or state in a painting or of an object due to the use of optical illusions, manipulated surfaces, or discordantly juxtaposed images.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
